OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghan teen girls despair  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fat unending Taliban school 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fban                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Teenage girls have told the BBC they   
OL,6, feel "mentally dead" as the Taliban's  
OL,7, ban on their education prevents them   
OL,8, from returning to school once again.   
OL,10,FMore than 900 days have now passed     
OL,11,Fsince girls over 12 were first banned. 
OL,13,FThe Taliban have repeatedly promised   
OL,14,Fthey would be readmitted once a number 
OL,15,Fof issues were resolved - including    
OL,16,Fensuring the curriculum was "Islamic". 
OL,18,FBut they have made little comment as a 
OL,19,Fthird new school year started without  
OL,20,Fteenage girls in class this week.      
